      "title": "About SOXY",
      "subtitle": "Our Story",
      "quote": "\"We are not just selling socks; we are simplifying your life.\"",
      "paragraph1": "I have worked in sock supply chains for a decade. I've seen the best socks sold at sky-high prices with logos, and the worst ones flooding street markets. My reason for founding SOXY is simple: break the profiteering, return to essence.",
